---
title: Saucy Beef & Cabbage Stir-Fry with Cilantro & Crispy Fried Onions
description: Falling into a stir-fry rut with the same veggie + sauce combo each week? We’ve got you covered. This version features garlicky ground pork, which is simmered in a sweet, savory, and spicy blend of umami ginger sauce, ponzu, sriracha, and rice wine vinegar. It’s tossed with tender sautéed cabbage, then spooned over jasmine rice and garnished with crispy fried onions and fresh cilantro. The best part? It’s ready in just 20 minutes from start to finish—now that’s what we call a winning dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66685b05cda025ae2c6f126c-6278fddd.jpeg
